<br>
I read a post that said it will port TARGETED group member (single) to their bind point with no confirmation required!  If this is true this spell is truely awesome!<br>
<br>
Can anyone with this spell confirm how it actually works?  I would love to have this spell the next time some annoying player keeps on bugging you to let them in your group!  hehe<br>
<br>
Lamor_1 says: &quot;Hey let me group with you until your other member arrives!  You only have five!&quot;<br>
Khalidah tells group: Invite this dork so I can translocate him.<br>
Khalidah giggles.<br>
Group member_2 tells group:  Khalidah you are nasty but I like it!<br>
Lamor_1 has joined your group.<br>
Khalidah targets lamor_1.<br>
Khalidah begins to cast translocate.<br>
<br>
On lamor_1 screen:<br>
Loading, please wait.<br>
You have entered North Freeport.<br>
WTF am I doing here?<br>
<br>
Khalidah types: /ignore lamor_1<br>
<br>
OH PLEASE LET THIS BE TRUE!<br>
<br>
Khalidah Arihant<br>
52 Channeler<br>
The Nameless <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ucaladdortalonthael.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Caladdor Talonthael</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/15/00 7:25:03 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.westerndecadence.org/photos/calthumb.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Translocate Clarification</span><hr size=1> Aye, a perfect way to banish somebody from a zone if they're not bound there. I guarantee we'll see a confirmation box coming up soon. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umanglodin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Manglodin </A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/15/00 11:37:55 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/eq_quartex/images/mang2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Translocate Clarification</span><hr size=1> It works like bind.  Target must be in your group.  You target that member, hit Translocate, and they are gated to thier own bind spot. <p>Manglodin Nightbringer <BR>
60th Sorcerer <BR>
Sol Invictus <BR>
The Tribunal 

</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ucaladdortalonthael.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Caladdor Talonthael</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/15/00 11:47:55 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.westerndecadence.org/photos/calthumb.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Translocate Clarification</span><hr size=1> Aye...I realize that. Trust me, the first thing I thought about when I heard of Translocate was &quot;Wow...I can use this to banish somebody annoying me.&quot; All they have to do is trust you enough to join your group and POOF! They're gone. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugherad.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gherad</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/15/00 1:12:29 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Translocate Clarification</span><hr size=1> It's really no different than being able to port people to Hate on a whim.  There is no confirmation box and if you wanted to screw over a melee class in your group, then you could.  Verant can't remove every possible way to harm another player without ruining the game.  They just have to assume that enough of you are adults and can solve your problems without exploiting things like that. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umysthyl.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mysthyl</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/15/00 2:18:52 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> hopefully no box</span><hr size=1> I have this spell and really like it. I do hope they don't put a confirmation box on it though. Right now its great for sending ppl home if they've fallen alseep on a raid. If you put in a confirmation box then that wouldn't work. It requires you to be grouped which is enough of a safty catch in my opinion.<br>
<br>
Mysthyl <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uororo7.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ororo7</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/17/00 7:24:03 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Where...</span><hr size=1> So where did you acquire the spell Mysthyl? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ubalrigard.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Balrigard</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/17/00 10:18:07 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where...</span><hr size=1> Just got mine out of IceWell Keep. And does rock!!<br>
<br>
Bal <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uhawkwinde.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hawkwinde</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/17/00 10:20:01 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where...</span><hr size=1> Got mine from Frostcube in dungeon under Icewell Keep, but it is not a common drop.<br>
<br>
Hawkwinde<br>
55th Circle of Growth<br>
Rodcet Nife <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugallenite.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gallenite</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/18/00 3:52:57 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ...</span><hr size=1> I've seen Translocate drop in Icewell, Velketor, and Necropolis so far.  One copy from each.<br>
<br>
No clue where the Castersrealm people got their info.<br>
<br>
Even the worst parsers out there showed it as a &quot;Port target to bind point&quot; spell from long before day one.  It's never said &quot;Full Group&quot; anywhere in there, afaik.<br>
<br>
<br>
Best,<br>
<br>
Gallenite<br>
The Pantheon<br>
Innoruuk <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uebinashelin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ebin Ashelin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/18/00 11:25:26 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...</span><hr size=1> i got my copy from a shambling cube in skyshrine. it conned blue, but was completely resistant to all magic. that particular shambling cube was much harder than any other 'shambling cube'.<br>
<br>
it is a single target spell.<br>
<br>
i would like to see a comfirmation box added, for anyone not in the group, giving us the option not to leave group to zap someone to thier bind point.<br>
<br>
also of extremely minor mention is that the spell has a yellow 'self only' gem, rather than a red 'targeted spell' gem. it is a single target spell. <p><center>
<img src=http://members.aol.com/forsweetkelly/ebinsig.jpg>
</center></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showMessage?topicID=21.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showMessage?topicID=11.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.emailToFriend?topicID=18.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.threadControl?topicID=18.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=18.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=18.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1">General Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm3">Trade Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm4">Rant Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm8">Mob Dropped Spells<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm10">Class Balance & Class Bugs<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm22">Out of Mana<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm27">PVP Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilat